  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Control:Override</strong> Is A Puzzle Game About <strong>Control</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/90de844486d042542bc526688a72e4c2.poster.avif?t=1752336661\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/90de844486d042542bc526688a72e4c2.webm?t=1752336661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/90de844486d042542bc526688a72e4c2.mp4?t=1752336661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/fc9e975468bc7e1f137dfe3cf1edb20e.poster.avif?t=1752336661\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/fc9e975468bc7e1f137dfe3cf1edb20e.webm?t=1752336661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/fc9e975468bc7e1f137dfe3cf1edb20e.mp4?t=1752336661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a <strong>hacker </strong>who has hacked into a <strong>rogue AI </strong>to <strong>terminate </strong>it.  <br>Abuse Physics to solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/8ad93158f08abc3ae3be7fa4e032a935.poster.avif?t=1752336661\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/8ad93158f08abc3ae3be7fa4e032a935.webm?t=1752336661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/8ad93158f08abc3ae3be7fa4e032a935.mp4?t=1752336661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve into a virtual cyberspace inside a rogue AI that YOU created in the past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Break through the AI's security layers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach the core.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terminate the AI. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>But Should You?</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/47b987a2ccfdb2990a844ae903cae64a.poster.avif?t=1752336661\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/47b987a2ccfdb2990a844ae903cae64a.webm?t=1752336661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/47b987a2ccfdb2990a844ae903cae64a.mp4?t=1752336661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong> Key Features </strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Simple mechanics. Unexpected consequences.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Physics defying puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A generous rewind mechanic that lets you fix your mistakes. Problem solving is an iterative process.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A minimalist neon art style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > An intriguing story of a hacker who hacked an AI of his own creation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiple endings that form a jigsaw puzzle-like narrative.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Control:Override</strong> Is A Puzzle Game About <strong>Control</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/90de844486d042542bc526688a72e4c2.poster.avif?t=1752336661\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/90de844486d042542bc526688a72e4c2.webm?t=1752336661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/90de844486d042542bc526688a72e4c2.mp4?t=1752336661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/fc9e975468bc7e1f137dfe3cf1edb20e.poster.avif?t=1752336661\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/fc9e975468bc7e1f137dfe3cf1edb20e.webm?t=1752336661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/fc9e975468bc7e1f137dfe3cf1edb20e.mp4?t=1752336661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a <strong>hacker </strong>who has hacked into a <strong>rogue AI </strong>to <strong>terminate </strong>it.  <br>Abuse Physics to solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/8ad93158f08abc3ae3be7fa4e032a935.poster.avif?t=1752336661\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/8ad93158f08abc3ae3be7fa4e032a935.webm?t=1752336661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/8ad93158f08abc3ae3be7fa4e032a935.mp4?t=1752336661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve into a virtual cyberspace inside a rogue AI that YOU created in the past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Break through the AI's security layers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach the core.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terminate the AI. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>But Should You?</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/47b987a2ccfdb2990a844ae903cae64a.poster.avif?t=1752336661\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/47b987a2ccfdb2990a844ae903cae64a.webm?t=1752336661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406090/extras/47b987a2ccfdb2990a844ae903cae64a.mp4?t=1752336661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong> Key Features </strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Simple mechanics. Unexpected consequences.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Physics defying puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A generous rewind mechanic that lets you fix your mistakes. Problem solving is an iterative process.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A minimalist neon art style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > An intriguing story of a hacker who hacked an AI of his own creation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiple endings that form a jigsaw puzzle-like narrative.</p></li></ul>",
